  <div class="flexible-content-page__top margin-horizontal margin-t-4">
    <div class="container max-width-2">
          <h1 class="article-title">The Lowy Institute Media Award</h1>
    <div class="article-intro intro-text">
      <p>Recognising Australian journalists who have deepened the knowledge, or shaped the discussion, of international policy in Australia.</p>

    </div>

    
          </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flexible-content-wrapper" >
            
